# Stray helper-script links created by the partest sandbox in subdirectories.
# A test that runs "python3 ../../simulate_fmu_fmpy.py ..." gets a deterministic
# symlink to the real (tracked) script left next to it; see
# testsuite/partest/runtest.pl:make_external_link(). The real script at the root
# of this directory is tracked and unaffected by these patterns.
**/simulate_fmu_fmpy.py
